<p>
    The Tonalities section is not just a tool for analysis but a gateway to understanding the complex interplay of harmony in music. By providing detailed insights into the tonal structures of songs and loops, it serves as an invaluable resource for music theorists, composers, and enthusiasts alike, fostering a deeper appreciation for the art and science of music.
</p>

